data.description: Country living with all the amenities just 3 minutes away from the Loop. This comfortable house has room to relax.  Each room is generously proportioned.  The pond is beautiful. The home welcomes you into a spacious living area, with a separate dining space on the right.  The kitchen opens to the living room.  The master bedroom is split from the other two bedrooms.  The bonus sunroom can accommodate many purposes, so you can use your imagination.  Beautiful built-ins can hold your things.  With 4.3 acres, this place has room for the garage, the shop, and plenty of space to spread out.  Make yourself at home, enjoying the view of your very own pond from the back deck large enough for parties.  There's nothing like this property available right now, and it's priced to move!
